column1: # Required | Unique Id for the item such as Sku Id | Max: 50 characters
column2: # Required | Title of the product. E.g. SKU Id | Max: 150 characters
column4: # Required | URL to product on your website
column5: # Required | URL to image of the product | JPEG and PNG only
column6: # Required | Current availability of the product | Supported values: in stock, out of stock, preorder, discontinued
column7: # Required | Price & currency of the product | Format: Price followed by currency code.  E.g. 19.90 USD
column8: #Required | Condition of the product at time of sale | Supported values: new, refurbished, used
column9: # Required | You can add either brand, mpn or gtin to this column. Only one of these values is required for this column
column10: # Optional | Supported values: newborn, infant, toddler, kids, adult
column12: # Optional | Supported values: male, female, unisex
column13: # Optional | Id for products that are variants of a specific product
column14: # Optional | Value from Google's product taxonomy | E.g. Home > Women > Dresses > Red Dresses
column15: # Optional | The category for the product | Home > Women > Dresses > Red Dresses
column16: # Optional | Whether the product contains adult content. | Supported values: Yes, No
column17: # Optional | Additional information about the product
column18: # Optional | Additional information about the product
column19: # Optional | Additional information about the product
column20: # Optional | Additional information about the product
column21: # Optional | Additional information about the product
column22: # Optional | Link to product's mobile optimized page | Used as webview fallback
column23: # Optional | URL of the App icon | Required for Deep Link and App Install creatives
column24: # Optional | Name of the iOS app | Required for Deep Link and App Install creatives
column25: # Optional | App Id on App Store | Required for Deep Link and App Install creatives
column26: # Optional | Deep Link URI to product | Required for Deep Link creatives
column27: # Optional | Name of android app | Required for Deep Link and App Install creatives
column28: # Optional | Android package | Required for Deep Link and App Install creatives
column29: # Optional | URL for app in Google Play Store | Deep Link URI to product | Required for Deep Link creatives
